import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"what-mri"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#what-mri"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`What MRI`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`这是一套集成开发环境`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`以 React + UMI + TypeScript + LESS 构成`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`以 Ant Design (React) 提供UI控件和设计风格`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`以 MasterRT补充部分UI和大部分的解决方案`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`以 THEME配置`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`以 CLI 辅助集成开发的前端研发项目`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"包含"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#包含"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`包含`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`MRI 主开发环境，包含 theme，route, components， widgets, commons 等`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`MasterRT UI组件以及部分解决方案`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`MRI-CLI `}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
